headline: ValuEngine Weekly Market Summary And Commentary
summary: The past week saw a clear defensive tilt across major ETFs. One notable reversal this month is that the Vanguard Value ETF (VTV) is up 0.75%, while its growth counterpart VUG is down 3.1%.
